Implement images using Podman - Practice using FROM , ADD, COPY , RUN , ENV , CMD and ENTRYPOINT Instructions.
Interact with live containers - mount directories from host, access them inside container.
Manage images - create Containerfile, build images, tag them, push them to a registry and use that image to spin up containers.
Run containers locally using Podman - Build an image and run 2 containers from same image.
  Multi stage build etc.
Run multi-container applications with Podman ( podman-compose ) - build and run a 3 tier app using compose file.
Troubleshoot containerized applications - 3 tier app , establish communication between containers connected via podman network. Frontend container
  to be reachable from a reverse proxy server
